{"title":"燃烧的黑眼睛","authors":["柯原"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":1,"day":26}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧的黑眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柯原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自华夏古老历史的积淀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一睁开就渴望燃烧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧毁了一个旧天地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托五星红旗冉冉上升"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亿万双黑眼睛汇集一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧着拚搏的毅力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧着创造的热情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃烧着对新世纪的信心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在贫瘠的土地上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汹涌着杂交水稻的金浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在茫茫沙漠中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萌动防护林带的青春"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同南极长城站的红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和南沙群岛高脚屋的星星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，黑眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天是港口飞扬的彩旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚是城市灿灿的明灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀万水千山的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有高高举起的亚运圣火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘荡城乡处处的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是歌唱祖国强大的心声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远向着未来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在世界的跑道上冲刺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着世纪扑面的晨风＊"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}